<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Internally all option keys are stored lowercase. The method hasOption() doesn't convert the given key to lowercase before looking it up.  This also affects the method getOption() which uses hasOption().</p>

<p>&lt;application.ini&gt;
[production]
phpSettings.display_startup_errors = 0
&lt;/application.ini&gt;</p>

<p>$bootstrap-&gt;hasOption('phpSettings') return false, should return true</p>

<p>$bootstrap-&gt;hasOption('phpsettings') returns true</p>

